    "title": "Uvivu na Kazi Ngumu",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "uvivu na kazi ngumu",
    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<p>Mungu aliumba Adamu na Hawa na kuwaweka katika Bustani ya Edeni ili kuitunza, siyo tu kupumzika na kuifurahia (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:15\">Mwanzo 2:15</a>). Kazi haikuwa adhabu baada ya wanadamu kutenda dhambi mara ya kwanza. Badala yake, Mungu alifanya kazi kuwa sehemu nzuri na yenye thamani ya uumbaji wake tangu mwanzo.</p><p>Kitabu cha Mithali mara nyingi kinakosoa uvivu (kutokuwa tayari kufanya kazi au kutokujitahidi wakati unapaswa). Mithali inafananisha watu wavivu na mlango unaosogea mbele na nyuma lakini hauendi popote (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov26:14\">Mithali 26:14</a>). Pia inafundisha kwamba watu wavivu ni wapumbavu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov22:13\">22:13</a>). Ukosefu wao wa kazi husababisha umaskini na kifo (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov6:6-Prov6:10\">6:6–10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:26\">10:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:19\">15:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov18:9\">18:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov19:15\">19:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov19:24\">24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov20:4\">20:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov21:25\">21:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov22:13\">22:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov24:30-Prov24:34\">24:30–34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov26:13-Prov26:16\">26:13–16</a>). Kinyume chake, watu wanaofanya kazi kwa bidii ni wenye hekima. Kazi yao husababisha kuwa na pesa za kutosha na maisha mazuri (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:4-Prov10:6\">10:4–6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov12:11\">12:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov13:4\">13:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov20:13\">20:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov31:10-Prov31:27\">31:10–27</a>).</p><p>Maana ya mwisho na utimilifu havitokani na kazi ngumu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl2:17-Eccl2:26\">Mhubiri 2:17–26</a>). Hatupaswi kusahau uwezo wa Mungu wa kutoa (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps127:2\">Zaburi 127:2</a>). Hata hivyo, hatuna kisingizio cha kuwa wavivu. Mungu alitubuni kutumia vipawa na uwezo wetu ili kuwa na tija, kujipatia riziki, na kuwasaidia wengine (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:28\">Waefeso 4:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:11-1Thess4:12\">1 Wathesalonike 4:11–12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess3:6-2Thess3:13\">2 Wathesalonike 3:6–13</a>).</p><p><u>Sehemu za Kujifunza Zaidi</u></p><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod23:12\">Kutoka 23:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov6:6-Prov6:11\">Mithali 6:6–11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:4-Prov10:6\">10:4–6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:26\">26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov12:11\">12:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov12:24\">24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov12:27\">27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov13:4\">13:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov13:11\">11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:4\">14:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:23\">23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:19\">15:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov18:9\">18:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov19:15\">19:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov21:5\">21:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov21:25\">25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov24:30-Prov24:34\">24:30–34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov26:13-Prov26:16\">26:13–16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov28:19\">28:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov31:10-Prov31:31\">31:10–31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl2:18-Eccl2:26\">Mhubiri 2:18–26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl4:5-Eccl4:6\">4:5–6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl5:12\">5:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl9:10\">9:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl11:4-Eccl11:6\">11:4–6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:11\">Warumi 12:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:28\">Waefeso 4:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:11-1Thess4:12\">1 Wathesalonike 4:11–12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess3:10-2Thess3:15\">2 Wathesalonike 3:10–15</a></p>",
